// SJMS 2.5 is OIDC-token-validated in server/src/middleware/auth.ts;
// no application code path read or wrote user_sessions rows
// (verified zero references across server/src and client/src under
// evidence/secrets-at-rest-2026-04-29.json on 2026-04-29). The model
// was removed under Option D of docs/security/secrets-at-rest.md to
